+# [[#Wyoming|Wyoming]]: [[Milward L. Simpson]] (R) was replaced by [[Clifford Hansen]] (R)

 === Republican gain ===
-# Oregon: [[Maurine Brown Neuberger]] (D) was replaced by [[Mark Hatfield]] (R)
+# [[#Oregon|Oregon]]: [[Maurine Brown Neuberger]] (D) was replaced by [[Mark Hatfield]] (R)

